 to go da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da,

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:13.400
 do its little thing here.

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:14.680
 And it's setting things up.

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:17.240
 Part of this is that there are hundreds of thousands

00:02:17.240 --> 00:02:18.560
 of people using Python Anywhere

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:21.360
 and it has to build your own interface.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:24.400
 Now, the dollar sign prompt is traditionally

