 directory and then work its way down.

00:07:02.760 --> 00:07:04.520
 So if you're like, where am I?

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:07.840
 You can say, go to tilde slash and then you know

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:09.880
 what that folder name is.

00:07:09.880 --> 00:07:13.560
 Let's see, do I have any files here?

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:16.280
 I can remove, let's go back into my home directory,

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:18.320
 do an ls and see some files.

00:07:18.320 --> 00:07:22.960
 DB.zap, let's just get rid of it, rm db.zap.

